---
layout: "layouts/home.njk"
---

{% from "macros.njk" import postList %}
{% set maxPosts = 3 %}
{% set maxMorePosts = 10 %}
{% set latestBlogPosts = collections.blog | head(maxPosts) %}
{% set latestStreamPosts = collections.stream | head(maxPosts) %}
{% set moreBlogPosts = collections.blog | slice(maxPosts, maxMorePosts) %}
{% set moreStremPosts = collections.stream | slice(maxPosts, maxMorePosts) %}

<section>
    <p>Hello! <strong><a href="/about">I'm Sean</a></strong>, a design technologist and software engineering leader who is interested in creative tools, tools for thought, malleable systems, the open web, human-computer interaction, sustainable computing, and generally anything related to making computers more inclusive, empowering, and convivial.</p>
    <p>This site is my blog and "<a href="https://maggieappleton.com/garden-history">digital garden</a>," a collection of <a href="/stream">quick thoughts</a>, <a href="/blog/">short essays</a> and <a href="/notes/">evergreen notes</a> on <a href="/tags/">topics</a> of personal interest.</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h2>Topics</h2>
    <ul class="tag-list">
    {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
        <li class="tag-list-tag"><a href="/tags/{{ tag | slug }}/">{{ tag }}</a></li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</section>
<section>
    <h2>Blog posts</h2>
    {{ postList(latestBlogPosts) }}
    {% if collections.blog.length > maxPosts %}
    <details>
        <summary>Show more…</summary>
        {{ postList(moreBlogPosts) }}
    </details>
    {% endif %}
</section>
<section>
    <h2>Thoughts in the stream</h2>
    {{ postList(latestStreamPosts) }}
    {% if collections.stream.length > maxPosts %}
    <details>
        <summary>Show more…</summary>
        {{ postList(moreStremPosts) }}
    </details>
    {% endif %}
</sections
